<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>另外，日本防卫省称，俄罗斯海军舰艇也于4日上午在钓岛附近毗连区航行。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


