            <title><![CDATA[台湾每周入境有望放宽到4万人次]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾入境防疫政策上个月放宽后，可能再进一步放宽，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>每周入境人数从现在的2.5万人次增至4万人次。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>综合《经济日报》、《联合报》报道，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾疫情指挥中心发言人庄人祥周六（7月2日）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>透露<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>自6月15日起放宽个人出入境后，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>指挥中心本周将开会探讨入境防疫政策，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>不排每周入境人数可从现在的2.5万人次增至4万人次。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>不过，庄人祥说明，讨论重点将放在入境人数是否放宽，对于“3+</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>4”的防疫天数是否可松绑至“0+7”，当局还需要斟酌。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>目前台湾入境防疫政策为“3+4”，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>即三天居家检疫及检疫期满后接续四天自主防疫，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>但是限制每周入境2.5万人次。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>庄人祥强调，对于入境管制的松绑仍需一步一步来，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>他形容目前台湾疫情还在“半山腰”，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>疫情发展与境外相比来得较晚，不太可能太早就松懈下来。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>由于正值旅游旺季，台湾民众出境需求大增，加上全球逐渐解封，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>入境需求也冲高。据台湾桃园机场出入境数据显示，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>当地暑假第一天周五（7月1日）的出境人数有6395人，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>入境有5077人。而放宽为“3+4”前，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>6月14日出境仅2789人，人数增长近三倍。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾交通部长王国材6月24日说，交通部经过盘点，防疫</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>德士<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>可承受入境5万人次的量能，防疫旅馆则可负担4.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>1万人次。在这推算下，他估计每周入境总量上限提升到4万人时，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>交通部仍可以承受。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<div id="innity-in-post"></div>
<div id="dfp-ad-midarticlespecial">
        
</div>



<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾前疾病管制局局长苏益仁表示，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾的冠病疫情自4月上旬开始上扬，至今已过三个月，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>而疫情高峰多半维持三至四个月，因此他预测，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾本土新增确诊人数到7月底，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>将降到3000例并维持这个数字。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>苏益仁建议，目前政府应该放宽出入境人数，“3+4”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>的防疫限制也应该取消，让疫情比照流感疫情，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>确诊者回归正常的医疗处置。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


